<P>
 Police arrested three men Wednesday on suspicion of stabbing an Oxnard man who 
remained in critical condition at St. John's Regional Medical Center in Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Tuan Le, 24, was attacked in the parking lot of a convenience store at the 
corner of 1st Street and Rose Avenue in Oxnard at 10:45 p.m. Tuesday, police 
