</P>
<P>
 Ventura (18-1) trailed, 25-18, heading into the 189-pound match, in which Ryan 
Burdick pinned Harvey Alvarado 3 minutes 44 seconds into the match. His older 
brother, Sean, pinned Frank Picos at 1:54 of the heavyweight match, sending the 
Cougars into the championship match next Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura defeated Royal, 51-15, and Camarillo, 39-26, earlier in the day to 
advance to the semifinal. GIRLS' BASKETBALL 
</P>
<P>
 Kennedy 64, Granada Hills 30 -- In their first game in more than a month, the 
Golden Cougars (13-4, 4-0) played at San Fernando High due to earthquake damage 
at the Kennedy gym. Kerri Garland had 10 points and 18 rebounds. 
</P>
