 Mojave 50, L.A. Baptist 41 -- Darlene Dotson and Debrah Weil scored 15 points 
apiece to lead Mojave (18-5) to a victory in a Division IV-A wild-card game at 
Brentwood. Darcie Frazier and Jody Weston led L.A. Baptist (12-10) with 14 
points apiece. 
</P>
