<HEADLINE>
<P>
FREEDOMS: THE ROLE PLAYED BY THE ACLU 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The letter from Andrea Saenz (Times, Feb. 3) was very impressive.It is 
encouraging to know that there are such young people who are aware of their 
freedoms guaranteed under the Constitution and are courageous enough to be 
outspoken about them. 
</P>
<P>
 Saenz may be interested to know that there exists an organization called the 
American Civil Liberties Union. One purpose of the ACLU is to offer legal 
assistance, when possible, to those who are willing to defend our Bill of 
Rights. 
</P>
<P>
 RONALD WEBSTER 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach 
</P>
